Package: llmapr
Type: Package
Title: A large language models mapper(mutli chat, analyze image and probe datbase)
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Yong Wang
Maintainer: The package maintainer <wangyong_cn@foxmai.com>
Description: A shiny app and library  for connect features of multi large language model, focused on MAP
    - M for multi models chats. chat with one or more models 
    - A for analyze picture using different models for analyzing image
    - P for probe database value, data and catalog based on large language and datbase.
